product_name: Anastasia Beverly HillsSmooth Blur Powder Bronzer
summary: SummaryHighlightsCruelty FreeBrilliant. Buttery. Bronzed. This ultra-smooth, luxuriously lightweight Smooth Blur Powder Bronzer features a blurring gel-powder hybrid formula that blends seamlessly into skin for long-lasting, natural matte color with a flawless, beautifully blurred, sun-kissed finish.
details: DetailsFeaturesSilky-smooth, lightweight bronzing powder with a rich, buttery textureDelivers sun-kissed color with a flawless, soft-matte finish for a natural glowBlurring, gel-powder hybrid formula seamlessly grips and blends with the skinHelps to blur the appearance of imperfections for a perfected complexionFinely-milled formula creates soft warmth for naturally bronzed skinCreamy, luxurious feel with a skin-like, non-powdery appearanceProvides long-lasting color with all-day comfortable wearabilityEnhances and sculpts the face with natural-looking warmth and definitionEffortlessly blends and builds evenly without patchiness, streaking, or settling in linesTrue-to-bronzing shades stay true to color and don‚Äôt shift or oxidizeCan be applied on bare skin or layered on top of makeup without disruptingHoused in a luxe, travel-ready component including a mirrorEasy to apply for all skill levels, including beginnerFree of: Gluten, Parabens, Phthalates, Mineral-Oil, Fragrance, Oil, SulfatesItem 2639980How To UseHOW TO APPLY:Using a powder brush, gently pick up a small amount of product. Apply to the areas of the face where the sun naturally hits: top of the forehead, temples, cheeks, and jawline. For a sun-kissed, glow, sweep across the center of the face and tip of the nose. Layer for desired intensity. Take it to the next level by applying to the body: under the chin, neck, top of the shoulders, and collarbone.‚ÄØPRO TIPS:For a natural bronze, select a shade that is 1-2 shades deeper than your skin tone.‚ÄØTap off the brush on the back of your hand before applying to the face.‚ÄØApply on bare face for a sun-kissed complexion.‚ÄØPair with A23 Pro Brush for a more targeted application.‚ÄØCan be used on the face and body.‚ÄØWorks beautifully alone or layered with cream, liquid, and powder formulas.‚ÄØSweep over bare lips for natural definition and contoured effect.‚ÄØIngredientsTalc, Zea Mays (Corn) Starch, Mica, Zinc Stearate, Dimethicone, Caprylyl Glycol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Silica, Kaolin, Plankton Extract, Polymethylsilsesquioxane, Maltodextrin, Echinacea Purpurea Extract, Citric Acid, Diamond Powder, Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), Ultramarines (CI 77007), Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Red 7 (CI 15850).Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details

reviews.headline: Great product
reviews.comments: Don't we all live a good bronzer. It covers all my dark spots. It helps complete my makeup look. Smells really well too. If I'm in the store I'm buying this.

reviews.headline: Real life filter
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] The blur is like a real life filter! Its application is super soft and easy to blend in. The packaging is super cute and there's not a prominent scent that I picked up. For my melanated girls, it doesn't look ashy with or without flash which i know is super important!

reviews.headline: Love the packing
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This bronzer is spectacular! Its super-resistant packaging protects the product very well. Its color is so beautiful and easy to blend. It doesn't have a scent, but its texture is very light and has a very natural finish..

reviews.headline: Perfect bronzer
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] beautiful shade, makes my cheeks looks with a little bit of blush, the powder can be manage easily, doesn't make your foundation come out, I loved the packaging with the imam

reviews.headline: Yes!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This bronzer is AMAZING!!! It's my new go to. It is silky smooth, the packaging is beautiful and it blends amazing. It really makes me look so sun-kissed.

reviews.headline: Smooth
reviews.comments: Okay this bronzer was super smooth, pigmented, and blended so easily. It didn't have a strong scent which was a plus for my sensitive skin. The packaging was also very sturdy usually these types of products come broken but this was good.

reviews.headline: Not my favorite
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I was not impressed with this product. First the color I chose was a little too dark but also it want a loose finish which I prefer. I found it harder to blend

reviews.headline: A bronzer that goes for the gold
reviews.comments: I absolutely love this bronzer that I received for free (in exchange for my honest review). It gives me a sun-kissed glow that I could only get from spending time on the beach or by the pool (which I probably won't because I'm a vampire, haha). This takes me back to my high school days, when bronzer was all the rage. It's like taking a little trip down memory lane every time I put it on. It's very matte, it blends with my other makeup well, and there is plenty of product. I will definitely be purchasing it again in the future! Thank you so much!

reviews.headline: Fabulous product and case is luxury
reviews.comments: I got to try this product and loved everything about this product. It works great as a bronzer but I also really love the case it comes in. Often now make up comes in cases that feel disposable and cheap, this is anything but that. It has a bit of weight and the mirror was much higher quality than others I have had. It is also just super cute.

reviews.headline: Great bronzer for everyday
reviews.comments: I received this product in exchange for my honest review. Loved this bronzer compact. It is a great size and love that is closes great. The color is nice as well and glides on perfectly. It is not powdery and blends well. The scent is nice as well not too strong which is great.

reviews.headline: Perfect shade
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] The perfect bronzer shade for my fair Asian skin!!! Usually it's too warm or too cool but this is the perfect shade for me and blends seamlessly. I love the compact since it comes with a mirror and opens and closes with ease but feels secure enough to bring with me if I needed to travel. Love it!

reviews.headline: Good Quality
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] The packing is pretty and feels luxurious but I do wish it was a little more durable. I had already scratched it after a week. The product itself is pretty good. It's buildable, blends well, doesn't have an overwhelming scent and lasts all day. It has more of a matte finish.

reviews.headline: I actually bought 2!
reviews.comments: I loved the shade I originally bought so I picked up the next shade up. both work very well for my skin tone. my new favorite bronzer as of right now :)

reviews.headline: Beautiful glow
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I love this Anastasia Beverly Hills bronzer! It gives me a gorgeous glow. like I've just spent a week on vacation in the sun, all without ever leaving my bedroom.

reviews.headline: Great bronzer
reviews.comments: Love this bronzer. The color is a bit dark for my complexion but it is very subtle as you will see in the pictures. I would probably go lighter next time. I received this item in exchange for my honest review. No scent on this one. The packaging is nice as well and you get a large bronzer for your money.

reviews.headline: Good bronzer
reviews.comments: If you're fair and looking for something warm but not oompa-loompa orange, this is a good choice. I like my bronzer to be more neutral, leaning cool, but this isn't too warm for me and it's beautiful on the skin. I'd say the description is actually really accurate, for once.

reviews.headline: Gorgeous color, but I wish it came with a brush!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This is a gorgeous bronzer in beautiful packaging, and it goes on very smoothly and blends easily. There's a lot to like about it, but I wish that it came with its own brush for the sake of convenience and portability!

reviews.headline: Fave bronzer of the moment
reviews.comments: This bronzer is soooo blurring and smoothing. I was so excited to receive this and it's made its way into my everyday makeup line up. The color is such a nice warm bronze without being overly orange and it's so pigmented without going on chalky or patchy. Love this bronzer!

reviews.headline: This bronzer rocks!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This bronzer is so pigmented,  a little really gives a long way. Its easy to blend and apply, the packaging feel super sturdy and luxurious, the finish is matte and has no scent! I definitely recommend this bronzer!

reviews.headline: Honestly perfect! üòç
reviews.comments: I received this product in exchange for my honest review and I can say that this was honestly the best bronzer I've ever tried. It's so seamless and blends super easily. It gives the perfect bronzy, warm and glowy look that you're looking for. Would definitely buy it again!

faceoff_positive.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Omg soo I am a huge fan of Anastasia Beverly Hills products, I've been using them since highschool. I was very excited to try this bronzer out. The formula is very lightweight and buttery. I love how it applies very seamlessly on my skin and looks natural. The bronzer is very easy to blend and the pigmentation is there so a little goes along way. I was amazed with this bronzer. üòçIt's very soft and has a matte finish so for me is perfect because I am an oily girl, but I still like my makeup to look softly natural and this bronzer helps me achieve that look. This bronzer is long lasted and I did not have any fallout. I like that with this bronzer, it doesn't look muddy or harsh it just looks smooth and bronzed. There is no scent to it so that is great. As for the shade range, they do offer a variety of shades and different undertones so I love that I didn't struggle with that. Okay and lastly, the packaging is absolutely gorgeous. It Gives off a very sleek and clean and clean aesthetic. Like it just screams that girl !!  It's travel size friendly and I love how the logo is on the bronzer and also on the packaging. The mirror is literally so for touchups. It is also very sturdy and a little thick so it gives it an extra layer of protection from breaking the product. This is definitely one of my new favorite bronzers and I will be recommending this one for sure.
faceoff_positive.headline: Obsessed

faceoff_negative.comments:
[I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I typically have fair skin with cool yellow undertones during the cold seasons except summertime. I have the color: beach bum bronze which is good match for my summer skin tone but too dark for fall or winter months.  The pigment intensity is rich and it leaves a nice matte finish.  The main ingredient is talc which provides the smooth texture and anti-caking texture. This color blends well and doesn't leave a total powdery mess in the sink area when I'm applying my makeup.

This compact is elegant however it is not lightweight. It is made out of metal so it's heavy. I wish this came in a smaller size option. I like how it is fragrance-free. It's made in Italy.
faceoff_negative.headline: Heavy
